    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "You have some options:\n\n- mix the indices, and make sure they have the same shape\n- use two different indices, with the index component in separate lists and have your UI distinguish between the two\n- use multi-index to search through both indices, then re-sort them frontend based on your own algorithm\n\nUnfortunately there's no builtin way to consolidate ranking across different criteria, as there's no way to sort those.",
